        "en": "You said that group work\ncan wait until we were all feeling more settled.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
