      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが全部断ってるんだよね\n取材依頼が一杯きてるみたいだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san has been turning down all the offers.\nSeems like there are a ton of interview requests.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.9507333463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "おかげでソロのお仕事とグループ練習に\n専念出来ています。感謝しないといけませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to that‚ we’ve been able to focus on our solo work\nand group practice. We should be grateful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、みんな\n相談したいことがあるんだけど……いいかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ everyone.\nI have something I want to talk about… Is that okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.0999982198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "渚？　どうしたんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa? What's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.8340963231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_moon-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 184.8813526021
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "今日の練習を見て思ったんだけど、私達もそろそろ\n四人でライブ出来るくらいになったんじゃないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was thinking after seeing everyone practice today‚\nmaybe we’re ready to do a live show as a four-member group?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.4146870798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "そう……ですね。確かに、今ある曲は一通り\n四人で出来るようになったと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's… true. We’re definitely able\nto perform all of our current songs with four members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.8333315532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "そろそろ練習以外でも、私達が成長するために\n何か出来ないかな、って思ってたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was thinking it’s time for us to do something outside of practice\nto help us grow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.0469998386,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわね。練習はあくまで練習\n人前に立ってこそアイドルですもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true. Practice is just practice after all.\nIt’s only when we stand in front of an audience that we’re truly idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.0666648865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "はいはーい！　それならさ、ライブバトルを\nいーっぱいしてみるのはどうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ yeah~!\nHow about we do a bunch of live battles?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.9999982198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "ライブバトル……？　通常のライブでも良さそう\nなものですけど、何か理由があるんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Live battles…?\nRegular live shows seem like they’d be fine too‚ but is there a reason you’re suggesting battles?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.0666648865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "えっとねー\nなんとなく！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um…\nI just feel like it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.5851369568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "相変わらず直感型ですわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're still so impulsive…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.0851358124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "……芽衣ちゃんの案、アリかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Mei-chan’s idea might actually be worth considering.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.3110315033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 240.7835445115
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、通常のライブも意味はあると思いますが\n私達のファンだけが見ている温かい場が多いですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ regular live shows have their own value‚ but…\nA lot of them are in warm settings where we’re only performing for our own fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.7333274842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "確かにそうかも。ライブはとっても楽しいけど……\n今の私達には、もっと別のやり方が必要だと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I guess you're right. Lives are a lot of fun but…\nI think we need a different approach right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.8266295303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんの強さは圧倒的でした。そしてあの二人は\nアイドル界で一番ライブバトルの経験を積んでいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "DoriKyun’s strength was overwhelming.\nAnd those two are the most experienced live battle competitors in the industry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 263.1333274842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、私達もライブバトルはやってきましたけど\n彼女達ほどの頻度で取り組んでいませんでしたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it’s true that we’ve done live battles‚\nbut we haven’t done them nearly as often as they have.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 271.5666608175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "模倣する必要はありませんが、同じフィールドに立つ\nことで私達の成長のヒントが見つかるかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We don’t need to copy them‚ but maybe by standing on the same stage‚\nwe can pick up some hints that’ll help us grow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 279.0666648865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "あくまで可能性があるというだけで\nどうなるかは分かりませんけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ that’s just a possibility.\nThere’s no guarantee it’ll work out that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 285.7333274842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどね、ライブバトルかー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ live battles‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 288.1841569453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "五人の時も調子が良くなかったから\n少し、心配だけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m a little worried because we weren’t doing so well\neven with five members…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 295.4216766057,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 297.750823612
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "とりあえずやってみようよ！　沙季ちゃんの言う通り\n四人で戦ったら、新しい発見があるかもよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s just give it a shot~! Like Saki-san said‚\nmaybe we’ll discover something new when we fight as a group of four.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 301.377972587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "それに……\n今の四人でどこまで出来るか、確かめてみたくない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides…\nDon’t you want to see how far we can go with our current members?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 306.6508247564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。もちろん、いきなりライブバトルに臨んで\n逆に心が折れる、なんていう危険もありはしますが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. Of course‚ there’s a risk we might end up demoralized\nif we jump into live battles too quickly‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 315.3666608175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_01-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "それなら問題ありませんわ",
      "translations": {
